  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay hidden among the crowd and defeat your opponents before getting spotted, or you risk not surviving in this <strong>party game</strong> where you need to mix <strong>stealth</strong>, <strong>speed</strong>, and <strong>tactics</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with 2 to 10 players, either locally or online, across 7 different game modes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/0965200ee29769817e72c1b6198582b7.avif?t=1732112230\" width=614 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/49a932fd6eadd7f04a30bca62186892f.avif?t=1732112230\" width=614 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the <strong>Target</strong> mode, each round presents a target that all players must find and kill. There is always one less target than the number of players, meaning the slowest to eliminate their target gets eliminated. The rounds continue until there is only one player left.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/a05e450a946d6bf54c82af0eb3af68e7.poster.avif?t=1732112230\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/a05e450a946d6bf54c82af0eb3af68e7.webm?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/a05e450a946d6bf54c82af0eb3af68e7.mp4?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/05bbcf67313f6762ab6e9a531acb0808.avif?t=1732112230\" width=614 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Battle Royale</strong>, players must stay inside a shrinking zone. If they go outside they are eliminated. The zone will keep moving and shrinking, and players can use their lightsaber to eliminate enemies. The last player standing wins the round.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/3f758b02a3e6d91cad815aa3550aff20.poster.avif?t=1732112230\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/3f758b02a3e6d91cad815aa3550aff20.webm?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/3f758b02a3e6d91cad815aa3550aff20.mp4?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/5025a34a0b1258b815eadf0ec5be5001.avif?t=1732112230\" width=614 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Domination</strong> is a tug-of-war mode where players work together to push an energy bomb into the opponent’s territory. The more players are in the zone, the faster they push the object. Players can eliminate enemies with lightsaber, and respawn 3 seconds after being killed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/65f0e217a1069ea36bbdbe0cf0737da8.poster.avif?t=1732112230\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/65f0e217a1069ea36bbdbe0cf0737da8.webm?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/65f0e217a1069ea36bbdbe0cf0737da8.mp4?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/7eb58a3842a99baad3d9b4e0df944da0.avif?t=1732112230\" width=614 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Race</strong> mode, the goal is to reach the finish line first. Players have 3 shots to eliminate characters they believe are controlled by other players. Each player is randomly assigned one of four abilities, and random events may occur in the arena.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/e0a3e86a84b45da988ef41cafe21220b.poster.avif?t=1732112230\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/e0a3e86a84b45da988ef41cafe21220b.webm?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/e0a3e86a84b45da988ef41cafe21220b.mp4?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/93fd5102e00780862ce4c7997f4111ef.avif?t=1732112230\" width=614 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Zombie</strong> mode, players must activate 4 computers while avoiding being hit by zombies. If a player is hit, they become zombified and can no longer activate computers, but they can infect other players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/d0212515fea66fd15a6e252494c19407.poster.avif?t=1732112230\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/d0212515fea66fd15a6e252494c19407.webm?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/d0212515fea66fd15a6e252494c19407.mp4?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/7e1069b7b17d77bcc330ae9c7b555317.avif?t=1732112230\" width=614 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Green Light</strong> mode, players must reach the finish line. But when the lights are on, players must stop moving to avoid being spotted, because the NPCs will never move. Players can use their 3 shots to eliminate characters they believe are other players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/f72e99e109d39e963de2be611665a3ab.poster.avif?t=1732112230\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/f72e99e109d39e963de2be611665a3ab.webm?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/f72e99e109d39e963de2be611665a3ab.mp4?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/b603356f514ff57a6201c207663721c4.avif?t=1732112230\" width=614 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Gold</strong> mode, golden statues appear each round, and players must touch a statue to survive. There is always one less statue than the number of players, and the player who fails to touch a statue is eliminated. The rounds continue until there is only one player left.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/0ee559a82d382395e0309036de9a27e5.poster.avif?t=1732112230\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/0ee559a82d382395e0309036de9a27e5.webm?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/0ee559a82d382395e0309036de9a27e5.mp4?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay hidden among the crowd and defeat your opponents before getting spotted, or you risk not surviving in this <strong>party game</strong> where you need to mix <strong>stealth</strong>, <strong>speed</strong>, and <strong>tactics</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with 2 to 10 players, either locally or online, across 7 different game modes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/0965200ee29769817e72c1b6198582b7.avif?t=1732112230\" width=614 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/49a932fd6eadd7f04a30bca62186892f.avif?t=1732112230\" width=614 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the <strong>Target</strong> mode, each round presents a target that all players must find and kill. There is always one less target than the number of players, meaning the slowest to eliminate their target gets eliminated. The rounds continue until there is only one player left.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/a05e450a946d6bf54c82af0eb3af68e7.poster.avif?t=1732112230\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/a05e450a946d6bf54c82af0eb3af68e7.webm?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/a05e450a946d6bf54c82af0eb3af68e7.mp4?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/05bbcf67313f6762ab6e9a531acb0808.avif?t=1732112230\" width=614 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Battle Royale</strong>, players must stay inside a shrinking zone. If they go outside they are eliminated. The zone will keep moving and shrinking, and players can use their lightsaber to eliminate enemies. The last player standing wins the round.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/3f758b02a3e6d91cad815aa3550aff20.poster.avif?t=1732112230\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/3f758b02a3e6d91cad815aa3550aff20.webm?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/3f758b02a3e6d91cad815aa3550aff20.mp4?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/5025a34a0b1258b815eadf0ec5be5001.avif?t=1732112230\" width=614 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Domination</strong> is a tug-of-war mode where players work together to push an energy bomb into the opponent’s territory. The more players are in the zone, the faster they push the object. Players can eliminate enemies with lightsaber, and respawn 3 seconds after being killed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/65f0e217a1069ea36bbdbe0cf0737da8.poster.avif?t=1732112230\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/65f0e217a1069ea36bbdbe0cf0737da8.webm?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/65f0e217a1069ea36bbdbe0cf0737da8.mp4?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/7eb58a3842a99baad3d9b4e0df944da0.avif?t=1732112230\" width=614 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Race</strong> mode, the goal is to reach the finish line first. Players have 3 shots to eliminate characters they believe are controlled by other players. Each player is randomly assigned one of four abilities, and random events may occur in the arena.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/e0a3e86a84b45da988ef41cafe21220b.poster.avif?t=1732112230\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/e0a3e86a84b45da988ef41cafe21220b.webm?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/e0a3e86a84b45da988ef41cafe21220b.mp4?t=1732112230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/93fd5102e00780862ce4c7997f4111ef.avif?t=1732112230